{"id": "1408543814506774588", "channel_id": "1408543814506774588", "type": 0, "author_id": "352428907468947474", "author_name": "sophiechoice", "author_bot": false, "content": "Some characters, like Horla and Jenkin for example, have Enlightens that change the way they play, sometimes in a way that might not be ideal for certain team compositions.\n\nI suggest adding the ability to toggle Enlightens to a lower level, maybe with a cooldown so that people can't abuse it?\n\nIt would also allow content creators to +12 a new unit for testing purposes, but then temporarily downgrade them to help showcase the character at lower investment levels.", "timestamp": "2025-08-22T20:10:14.857000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-08-22T20:17:03.285000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "thumbsup", "emoji_id": "1356086340298473574", "count": 18}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1408543814506774588", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「Answered」Suggestion: Please allow us to toggle Enlightens!", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1361168939622727801"]}
